		<td><b>Voices in Gradius II</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I just met with the last boss of Gradius II tonight, wich is an horrible mutant giant head. When you approach him, the music changes, and his moth animates playing some noise that sound like an ogre's voice trough the DPCM channel for quite a while, before starting to attack.
<br />
<br />By silenting all channels but DPCM and replay the sample at a faster rate, I found this kinda amusing : The last boss says "Speed up - Missile - Double - Laser - *pause* - Laser - *pause* - Speed up - Missile - Double - Laser" (with slowed down voice to sound ugly) when you encounter him.
<br />
<br />As a proof that memory limitation can turn into amazing trivia.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


